*Uši* su joj bile dugačke i tanke. (Her ears were long and thin.)

Mali je nosio kapu sa širokim *ušima*. (The boy was wearing a cap with wide ears.)

Ona je imala *uši* kao miš. (She had ears like a mouse.)

Tišinu je prekinuo šuštanje *ušiju*. (The silence was interrupted by the rustling of ears.)

On je lupkao *ušima* kada je čuo zvuk. (He flapped his ears when he heard the sound.)

*Uši* su joj se dižu kada je uplašena. (Her ears go up when she is scared.)